name: Miladogrph No.101
description:
The project "Miladograph" has been started in a journey. When I was going though depression and mental breakdown, I left my bustling city to move to a beautiful small town. The beauty that saved me from the very verge of breakdown. So I made my decision to picture the lost saving attractions of my new place of residence to share them with others.
And "Miladograph" was born.
